%I A393741 #9 Mar 07 2026 05:48:47
%S A393741 1,1,4,21,183,1905,22631,285140,3747178,50741181,703817922
%N A393741 Number of free polyominoes in the {8,5} tessellation of the hyperbolic plane.
%F A393741 a(n) = P{p,q}(n) (the number of {p,q} polyominoes of size n) is equal to P{p,oo}(n) for n <= q; also P{p,q}(q+1) = P{p,oo}(q+1) + floor((p-1)/2) - floor((3+q(p-2))/2). In this case, p=8, q=5 and P{p,oo} = A389937.
%Y A393741 Cf. A393739, A393740, A393742, A393743, A393744, A389937.
%K A393741 nonn,more,new
%O A393741 1,3
